OL,3,CSynagogue's 150 year anniversary hopes
OL,4,Cto unite communities
OL,6,FIt is the only Jewish museum in
OL,7,FEngland outside London and is home to
OL,8,Fat least 31,000 artefacts, which show
OL,9,Fwhat the Jewish community's given to
OL,10,FManchester and how its communities
OL,11,Fhave changed through the years.
OL,13,FThe Spanish and Portugese synagogue
OL,14,Fhas been fully restored after years of
OL,15,Fhard work.
OL,17,FIt closed in 1982 and re-opened as a
OL,18,Fmuseum in 1984. In 2019 it had a #6
OL,19,Fmillion redevelopment which saw it
OL,20,Fdouble in size with an added annexe.
