OL,3,CSynagogue's 150 year anniversary hopes
OL,4,Cto unite communities
OL,6,FDuring the redevelopment the team
OL,7,Ffound a time capsule on the site.
OL,9,FCurator Alex Cropper explains what was
OL,10,Finside:
OL,12,F"It contained six newspapers, some
OL,13,Fcoins and a beautiful document that
OL,14,Fdescribes the day and who was at the
OL,15,Fceremony for the laying of the
OL,16,Fcornerstone"
OL,18,FThe museum explains the history of the
OL,19,Fsephardi community who came to worship
OL,20,Fat the Synagogue.
