OL,3,CSynagogue's 150 year anniversary hopes
OL,4,Cto unite communities
OL,6,F"Jewish and Islamic communities have
OL,7,Fso much in common and have such a
OL,8,Fshared history of living peacefully
OL,9,Ftogether for thousands of years so if
OL,10,Fwe can help bring that message to
OL,11,Fpeople and show that there is far more
OL,12,Fthan unites our diverse communities
OL,13,Fhere in Manchester than divides us, if
OL,14,Fwe can use our 150th anniversary to
OL,15,Fgive that message then that can only
OL,16,Fbe a positive thing"
OL,18,FAs part of the celebrations a new time
OL,19,Fcapsule is being laid at the Synagogue
